t werden sowohl musikalische und literarische Aspekte des Repertoires als auch Fragen der Funktion und Aufführungssituation. Die Studie beinhaltet darüber hinaus eine kommentierte Werkbiographie sowie Transkriptionen von Notenmaterial.  aThis interdisciplinary cultural historical study is devoted to the intellectual biography of the journalist and poet, Georg Greflinger (ca. 1617–1677), a fascinating and in many respects exemplary author of 17th century German literature and musical history. The focus is on Greflinger’s song lyrics – the area in which the author achieved the greatest recognition during his own epoch and beyond.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aAuthors, Germany17th centuryvBiography. 0aSongszGermanyy17th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aCasualia. 4aGreflinger. 4aLied. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 17th Century.2bisacsh  aSong.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1z978311076251808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2015z9783110438673oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831103915580 cprintz978311036336440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311036340140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110363401423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110363401/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076251-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKUb2015